                     <interp inst="t18300916-187-person1573" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a butcher. On the 21st of August the prisoner called at my shop and asked my permission to weight a sirloin, and some other pieces he had sold, and he asked me to buy some at 2s. 6d. a stone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-187-person1574">
