                     <interp inst="t18300916-187-person1574" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a butcher, and live in Cow-cross-street - he came to me and asked if I would buy<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183009160089"></xptr>some meat - I said No - he threw it on the block and left it.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put is a paper, stating that he was intoxicated when he committed the offence; he received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY.</p>
